When the Constitution hangs by a thread… will you even recognize your role?
In this conversation, Hannah Stoddard (Director of the Joseph Smith Foundation) unpacks what Joseph Smith actually taught about the Elders of Israel, the Kingdom of God, and why the Book of Mormon is a survival manual for our day.

This episode will challenge how you see the last days, gathering of Israel, the fall of America and the Constitution, Zion, and your responsibility to defend — not just survive.
See more videos by Hannah on her channel here: https://www.youtube.com/c/JosephSmithFoundation

